---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Progress Spinner
description: an indeterminate spinning progress indicator
---

{% from "components/progress-spinner/macro.njk" import progressSpinner %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>{{ progressSpinner({}) }}</p>

<h2>With custom label</h2>
<p>{{ progressSpinner({ label: "Saving…" }) }}</p>

<p>{{ progressSpinner({ label: "Checking availability…" }) }}</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The macro sets
  <code>role="status" aria-live="polite" aria-busy="true"</code>
  and always emits an <code>aria-label</code> (default "Loading"),
  so the spinner is announced when it appears.</p>
